node.title: Latest on COVID from around the world: Number of patients in intensive care in France has fallen for second day
node.description: Here is the latest COVID news from around the world.
node.content: ["A surge in coronavirus cases caused by the Omicron variant may have peaked in some parts of Europe but medics say the impact will continue to be felt across the region, with hospitals still at risk of facing a rush of admissions.", "Reuters"]
